==English==
===Etymology===
*[[poly-]] + [[form]]

===Noun===
'''polyform''' (''plural'' '''polyforms''')

#{{mathematics}} A [[plane]] or [[solid]] [[figure]] constructed by joining together identical [[polygon]]s edge to edge.

